  "type": "spr",
  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">During a 5-second time interval, the average acceleration <span class=\"italic\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_style:italic \">a</span></span>, in meters per second squared, of an object with an initial velocity of 12&nbsp;meters per second is defined by the equation <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a equals, the fraction with numerator v subscript f, end subscript, minus 12, and denominator 5\"></span></span>, where <span class=\"italic\">v</span><sub><span class=\"italic\">f</span></sub> is the final velocity of the object in meters&nbsp;per&nbsp;second. If the equation is rewritten in the form <span class=\"italic\">v<sub>f</sub></span> = <span class=\"italic\">xa</span> + <span class=\"italic\">y</span>, where <span class=\"italic\">x</span> and <span class=\"italic\">y</span> are constants, what is the value of <span class=\"italic\">x</span> ?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [],
  "keys": [],
  "rationale": "<p>The correct answer is 5. The given equation can be rewritten in the form <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"v subscript f equals, x a, plus y\"></span>, like so:<p>\n        <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, equals, the fraction with numerator v subscript f, end subscript, minus 12, and denominator 5\"></span></p><p>\n        <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"v subscript f, end subscript, minus 12, equals 5 a\"></span></p><p>\n        <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"v subscript f equals, 5 a, plus 12\"></span></p><p>It follows that the value of <span class=\"italic\">x</span> is 5 and the value of <span class=\"italic\">y</span> is 12.</p></p><!--EndFragment-->\n",
